abstract: The Corner blog of The National Review mixed up the original publication date of Ms. Warren’s book.
snippet: The Corner blog of The National Review mixed up the original publication date of Ms. Warren’s book.
lead_paragraph: In a post marked 6 p.m. Friday, The National Review’s Web site The Corner made a potential bombshell accusation against Elizabeth Warren, the Democratic candidate for Senate in Massachusetts — that Ms. Warren was a plagiarist.

headline.main: Plagiarism Charge Against Elizabeth Warren Made, Then Quickly Dropped
